<paragraph blockId="0.[146,1431,1461,2028]" pageId="0" pageNumber="9">The new species is characterized by its suborbicular leaf lobes, crenulate-denticulate lobe margins, the rough dorsal surface of the leaf lobes and the two-celled lobule. This combination of characters is quite distinct and separates it from all congeners.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
